{"tid":1077134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（長文慎入）單程證否決權大行動","createTime":"2019-03-25T11:29:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T09:50:24.000Z","uid":104965,"like":72,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b22e54de629f134e9fbdd8cacbe8410d85567bc8","tid":1077134,"uid":104965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:29:45.000Z","msg":"睇完隔離個post 話澳門都可以否決單程證人士定居<br />\n<br />\n覺得香港都應該立法咁做<br />\n<br />\n邊個議員反對或棄權就是人民公敵<br />\n<br />\n而家唔係每個單程證都要否決<br />\n<br />\n香港只係要確定呢個權利<br />\n<br />\n香港唔係收容港<br />\n<br />\n你說我們悍衛自己的土地是法西斯？<br />\n我就大大聲係條街度叫：我係法西斯！<br />\n<br />\n你罵我們保護自己的醫療系統是法西斯？<br />\n我就大大聲係條街度叫：我係法西斯！<br />\n<br />\n指責我們愛護自己的司法制度是法西斯？<br />\n我就大大聲係條街度叫：我係法西斯！<br />\n<br />\n怒斥我們守護自己的本土文化是法西斯？<br />\n我就大大聲係條街度叫：我係法西斯！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我們就是一班守護及愛護香港的法西斯！<br />\n法西斯不可恥！<br />\n可恥是一班打著大愛旗號賣港求榮的偽術黨！"},{"pid":"ff8cab2cba56dbaaf982ae200825d52133489f47","tid":1077134,"uid":104965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:41:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af31ffe5a2c44069a2b2d01c980620e6acbe22bf","tid":1077134,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:33:22.000Z","msg":"光復審批權無違反人道原則。"},{"pid":"da886941b30d8c9695271adea5b81f53794ab503","tid":1077134,"uid":97603,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T13:22:13.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"c9a0cad66a9f37e199d1b9daacf7bdbb33ae90c7","tid":1077134,"uid":144201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T13:22:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"53232af743617016e076cc752386746708fc2e17","tid":1077134,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T13:26:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"701a87753b4d7c6192e95d24c8e1e5b1ce80d77f","tid":1077134,"uid":70830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T13:27:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b1fd5948f3f2e2dc5ee6997391e5c3ee55ac1e","